>) has kept pace and looks set to challenge its all-time high of $55 next year. This</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1001776014/image_1001776014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743561-bank-of-america-buy-now-for-increased-dividends", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:04:15"}, {"id": "4743506", "title": "SP500 Likely To Underperform In 2025, But Still One Of The Best Long-Term Investments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"S&amp;P 500 stock market index crash and bear market due to financial crisis and recession in US. Wooden blocks in with coins in dark black background.\" data-id=\"1420095549\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420095549/image_1420095549.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><fi