3.70% for the quarter, underperforming the 8.41% return of the Russell 2000 Growth Index. <span></span> For the three-month period, consumer discretionary, financials, and energy were the largest contributors to performance.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180674755/image_2180674755.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743563-allspring-small-company-growth-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 16:15:00"}, {"id": "4743549", "title": "Aligos Therapeutics: Promising Pipeline With Cash And Dilution Risks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Paper craft Liver\" data-id=\"1163730687\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163730687/image_1163730687.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcapti